data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Chateau At Antelope Ridge community! This stunning ranch style home situated on a corner lot is sure to impress with its 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage, and ample 1,481 square footage. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a tile entry and a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for relaxing on cool evenings. Plus, the stainless steel appliances in the kitchen make cooking a breeze! But the real showstopper is the walkout to the back deck - imagine sipping your morning coffee while soaking up the gorgeous Colorado scenery. And with a partially covered wood deck and raised garden bed, you'll have everything you need to create your own personal oasis. The large primary bedroom is the ultimate retreat, complete with an indulgent 5-piece ensuite that includes a double vanity and jetted soaking tub. Talk about luxury living! And let's not forget about the amazing community amenities, including a club house, playground, pool, picnic area and basketball courts. Plus, with no shared walls, this condo-style living experience truly offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this incredible home yours. Contact us today and schedule a tour - your dream home is waiting!
